  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2018-07-26",
    "date": "2019-04-18T13:21:50Z",
    "text": "Protecting Taxpayers Act\n\n This bill modifies the organizational structure, management practices, and enforcement procedures of the Internal Revenue Service (IRS).\n\nThe bill modifies policies regarding:\n\n the IRS Oversight Board, employee training procedures, tax enforcement procedures, various tax requirements that affect small businesses, the correction of errors by retirement plan administrators, programs that assist low-income taxpayers, the IRS appeals process for taxpayers, and information technology."
